subject: Beach Volleyball
lead_paragraph: The Olympic gold medalists Misty May-Treanor and Kerri Walsh won their fourth straight AVP Crocs Tour Manhattan Beach Open, beating Jen Boss and April Ross, 21-18, 21-16. May-Treanor and Walsh also clinched the the season championship and pocketed $100,000, the top winner’s check in beach volleyball history.
